attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: {"prompt": "Configure model-driven telemetry for EVPN on IOS XR with server 10.10.10.10:57000, tcp, sample interval 30000ms."}
attributes.mlflow.spanOutputs:
"telemetry model-driven
 sensor-group EVPN-TELEMETRY
  sensor-path evpn/standby/teps
  sensor-path evpn/standby/evi-detail/evi-children/route-targets/route-target/evpn-instance
  sensor-path evpn/standby/evi-detail/evi-children/ethernet-auto-discoveries
  sensor-path evpn/standby/teps/tep
  sensor-path evpn/standby/evi-detail/evi-children/ethernet-auto-discoveries/ethernet-auto-discovery/path-buffer/sr-te-info
  sensor-path evpn/standby/evi-detail/evi-children/macs/mac/path-buffer/sr-te-info
  sensor-path evpn/active/teps
  sensor-path evpn/active/evi-detail/evi-children/route-targets/route-target/evpn-instance
  sensor-path evpn/active/evi-detail/evi-children/macs/mac/path-buffer/sr-te-info
 !
 destination-group DG-GRPC
  address-family ipv4
   destination 10.10.10.10
    port 57000
    encoding self-describing-gpb
    protocol grpc no-tls
 !
 subscription SUB-EVPN
  sensor-group-id EVPN-TELEMETRY sample-interval 30000
  destination-group-id DG-GRPC
 !"
